      <title>高盛支持的市场初创公司扩大其银行业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/goldman-backed-marketplace-startup-expands-its-banking-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Olist 是一家巴西初创公司，帮助 40,000 名客户在大型市场平台上销售产品，该公司正在进军银行业务，以提高客户效率，同时为企业创造新的收入来源。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/goldman-backed-marketplace-startup-expands-its-banking-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 14:00:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称 Northvolt 将推迟瑞典 IPO 至明年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/northvolt-is-said-to-push-back-sweden-ipo-to-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，电池制造商 Northvolt AB 计划明年在瑞典上市，此前该公司曾预计首次公开募股 (IPO) 可能会在 2024 年进行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/northvolt-is-said-to-push-back-sweden-ipo-to-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 13:40:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
